wikipedia_page.main: Captain Joshua David Gerald Chaytor (13 May 1903 – 4 March 1937) was an Irish-born  cricketer. A right-handed batsman and right-arm fast-medium bowler, he played first-class cricket in the 1924 English cricket season and also represented the Egypt national cricket team.
